<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #4b5563;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #ecfdf5 100%);
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 24px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #15803d 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 48px 32px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header-icon {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        border-radius: 16px;
        margin: 0 auto 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 28px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 40px 32px;
      }

      .content h2 {
        color: #1f2937;
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .success-info {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 100%);
        border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
        border-left: 6px solid #16a34a;
      }

      .success-info h3 {
        color: #15803d;
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .security-tips {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }

      .security-tips h3 {
        color: #1e293b;
        margin: 0 0 16px 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .tips-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;
      }

      .tips-list li {
        padding: 8px 0;
        color: #374151;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 32px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #6b7280;
        font-size: 14px;
        background: #f9fafb;
        border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container { margin: 20px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-icon">✅</div>
        <h1>Password Updated</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2>Password Changed Successfully</h2>

        <div class="success-info">
          <h3>✨ All Set!</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: #15803d; font-weight: 500;">Your password has been successfully updated. Your account is now secured with your new password.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="security-tips">
          <h3>🔐 Security Reminders</h3>
          <ul class="tips-list">
            <li>🔒 Keep your password confidential</li>
            <li>🌐 Always log out from shared computers</li>
            <li>📱 Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
            <li>⚠️ Contact us if you notice any suspicious activity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="color: #6b7280; text-align: center; margin-top: 24px;">
          If you didn't make this change, please contact our support team immediately.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated security notification for <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong></p>
        <p>If you have any concerns, please contact our support team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
